<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Charles_Sanders_Peirce&amp;action=edit&amp;section=37" title="Edit section: Information, inquiry, logic, semiotics">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Information, inquiry, logic, semiotics</span></h3>
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="multicol" style="background:transparent; width:100%;">
